results.name: Number of self-complementary 2-graphs with n nodes.
comment: Sozański (1980, p. 141) says: "Note that formula (20) also gives the number of isomorphism classes of self-complementary p-point two-graphs." Formula (20) apparently refers to sequence A263626 (according to the references there). Is this sequence the same as A263626? (This would mean a(n) = 0 for 3 == n mod 4.) - _Petros Hadjicostas_, Feb 27 2021
